Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
list_gui_marker(25.10)                                  list_gui_marker(25.10)

Name
       list_gui_marker - Gives a list of GUI markers in the design layout

Syntax
       list_gui_marker

       Gives a list of GUI markers in the design layout.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description of the list_gui_marker command.

              For  a detailed description of the command, use the man command:
              man list_gui_marker.

Example
              * The following command shows a list of GUI markers:

                list_gui_marker

                The following is displayed:

                {name:aa  coordinate:(100.000 100.000)}

Related Information
              * add_gui_marker

              * remove_gui_marker

